      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……あ、葵！　良かった、やっと見つけた\n随分探したんだからな……はぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… Ah‚ Aoi! Thank goodness‚ I finally found you.\nI’ve been looking everywhere for you… haa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.9541040738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、{user}君？　どうしたのさ\nそんなに息切れして、運動不足なんじゃないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ {user}-kun? What’s wrong?\nYou’re that out of breath—aren’t you out of shape?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1487725413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、葵よりは運動不足かもしれないけど……\n……じゃなくて、葵を呼びに来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I might be more out of shape than you…\n…But that’s not the point. I came to get you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影中にふらっといなくなって慌ててたら\n莉央さんが、この公園にいるかもって教えてくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you suddenly disappeared during the shoot‚ we panicked\nand Rio-san said you might be in this park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.380997308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "だって、いきなり機材トラブルだって言うしさ\n復旧するまで、ただ待ってるのも暇だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ they suddenly said there was equipment trouble.\nJust waiting around until it’s fixed is boring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "で、近くに公園があったのを思い出して\n久々にここで踊るのも悪くないかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I remembered there’s a park nearby.\nI thought dancing here again after so long wouldn’t be bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5047160465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9732648212
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵らしいな……でも、故障はなんとかなったらしい\n撮影も再開するから、ロケ場所に戻ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s so like you… but it seems the malfunction’s been fixed.\nFilming’s starting again‚ so let’s head back to the location.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0512012162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、もう少し休憩時間延びない？\nこんな短い時間じゃ、踊った気がしないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ can’t the break be a little longer?\nWith such a short time‚ it doesn’t even feel like I danced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
